text: Claude Darciaux (born October 18, 1942) was a member of the National Assembly of France. She represented Côte-d'Or's 3rd constituency, from 1997 to 2012 as a member of the Socialiste, radical, citoyen et divers gauche. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:People from Besançon Category:Politicians from Bourgogne-Franche-Comté Category:Socialist Party (France) politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
title: Claude Darciaux
